<br>
LDoN not yet has much to offer for EP+ players.  I think it is great for mid - high level players who don't have the pleasure to play 24/7 and in a hardcore EP+ raiding guild.  PoP took care of those 24/7 players already.  LDoN is for players to fool around with friends for couple of hours daily and maybe eventually find something that they can use for their chars without rely on a guild to raid ssra+. <p><!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:maroon;font-family:comic sans;"><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=376166" target="top"><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Raiya Lemmingwarden</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></a><!--EZCODE LINK END--></span><!--EZCODE FONT END--><br>
